            UIC Business Alumni
          Heading link



 
Copy link



As a UIC Business alum, you are one of more than 37,000 men and women who are linked to an influential business network. Even after graduation, our alumni continue to be actively involved with UIC Business and its students – both on and off campus.
UIC Business alumni serve as mentors for current students, as volunteer in Alumni 4 U, and speakers for the Executives in the Classroom and the Business Career Center. They host students at their place of work or take them out to dinner for networking opportunities.
They love UIC Business and the opportunities it presented to them, so they make every effort to keep their Flames spirit alive by giving students access to experiences that enhance their business education.






