            Business Advisory Council
          Heading link



 
Copy link



UIC Business enjoys support from a Business Advisory Council that works with the dean to provide: ambassadorship and advocacy, pre-professional mentoring of UIC Business undergraduates, and practical business perspectives and advice.  The BAC is composed of leaders from the business world including UIC Business alumni as well as friends who attended other colleges.  For more information, please contact Michaela Smith Esboldt, Associate Director of Engagement and Participation at UIC Business, at mmsmith1@uic.edu or (312) 996-5916.





